org.bytedeco.javacpp

Class avutil.AVDownmixInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.javacpp.avutil.AVDownmixInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    avutil

    public static class avutil.AVDownmixInfo
extends org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
    This structure describes optional metadata relevant to a downmix procedure. All fields are set by the decoder to the value indicated in the audio bitstream (if present), or to a "sane" default otherwise.
